  "synopsis": "The nation's buzzing about Ahn Su-Ho, the newly awakened player who's giving up a life of riches to become a civil servant. They don't realize that Su-Ho's been a civil servant before... in his past life before he was killed by his own team! Now, Su-Ho's out to save the country from the worst of its criminal scum by gaining the strength to stop them before they can strike. Can Su-Ho power up and protect the nation, even if it means starting over completely? Or will justice be thwarted once more?\n\n(Source: Tapas)",
